if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('base_productsku')
and type = 'U')
drop table base_productsku
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: base_productsku */
/*==============================================================*/
create table base_productsku (
SkuID int identity(100000,1),
ProID int not null,
Code nvarchar(100) null,
Num int not null,
SWeight int null,
PurPrice decimal(10,2) null,
SaltNum int null,
Status int not null,
Warning int null,
IsDel bit not null default 0,
AddTime datetime not null default getdate(),
PicUrl nvarchar(200) null,
constraint PK_BASE_PRODUCTSKU primary key (SkuID)
)
go
